The '''multipede''' was a creature of [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. According to proverb, upon thinking about what it was doing, it would forget to walk.

{{Stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The proverbial Corellian multipede is a reference to the real-world concept of [[Wikipedia:The Centipede's Dilemma|The Centipede's Dilemma]].

